Name: Gold and Turquoise Slub Silk Embroidered Anarkali
Description: Look stunning in this gold and turquoise slub silk anarkali gown adorned in gold, turquoise and pink thread work embroidery, the anarkali has a beaturiful pink floral embroidery design. The anarkali is underlinned with santoon fabric and comes with a chiffon dupatta and santoon fabric bottom.

Name: Pink and Gold Uppada Silk Embroidered Anarkali
Description: This pink uppada silk anarkali embroidered in gold threadwork is an elegant gown. This dress is double layered with gold lacework embroidered broder at the hem, the skirt is attached bodice with pleats from the waistband giving the skirt its flare. This anarkali is underlined with Santoon fabric and comes with Santoon fabric pants and Chiffon dupatta.

Name: Red Georgette with Heavy Gold Embroidered Border Anarkali
Description: The gorgeous red georgette anarkali with a heavy embroidered gold border will make anyone standout from the crowd. The bodice gives the illusion of a separate jacket piece, the bodice is attahed to the skirt. This gown comes with achiffon dupatta and santoon fabric pants.
